response.overview: The Athletic Model Guild (AMG) was the patriarch of "physique" photographers. In a half-century of photographing nude young men, AMG's Bob Mizer produced thousands of charming, surprisingly moralistic movies. Join us in taking a look back at this bygone era of innocent sexuality.
response.tagline: Return with us to a time when "Dirty Movies" were just good, clean fun!
response.title: AMG The Fantasy Factory
